2003-05-05 11:04  chregu

	* components/transformers/libxslt.php:

	utfHack. very ugly, but we had some problems with not proper encoded stuff..
	
	the parameter:
	 <map:parameter type="options" name="utfHack" value="true"/>
	
	will just replace all chr(4) with "". This solved my problems...
	
