2003-04-01 12:56  chregu

	* components/selector.php:

	- do not set maps for selector hits
	This could make our sitemap not working anymore.
	if you used somethign like {../value} in a <map:select><map:when> part
	you have to change this to {value}, since there is no map-return from selector
	matches anymore
	
