2003-03-31 16:46  hannes

	* components/generators/usercomments.php:

	
	
	Some steps towards threaded discussions: Every URL now gets assigned a forum, not a thread.
	We also don't need the mapping table anymore.
	You can chose to have threaded or flat discussions in sitemap.xml, but we still need to fix some templates to make this acutally work.
	Multiple languages work now.
	It seems like I introduced a new bug: error messages don't disappear, even if everything works fine in the second try. I'm checking
	this in these minutes, just committing to allow chregu to have a look at what I've tinkered.
	
