2003-02-24 19:29  chregu

	* components/generators/structure2xml.php:

	finally, http caching for type="aggregate" in your structure.xml
	
	you have to enable st2xmlCaching in the sitemap and then http-requests are
	cached. the entry in structure.xml should look like:
	<bxst:section name="blog" type="aggregate" src="http://blog.bitflux.ch/b2rdf.php"
	expires="access minus 1 day"
	/>
	
	this means, it only checks every 24 hours, if the remote page changed. if you
	leave out expires attribute, it will check every hour.
	
	It checks for 304 answers and compares the response, if there's a 200 answer
	from the remote server.
	
	TODO: expires should also be used for db-checking (means, only check db every hour
	for change...)
	
	TODO: additionally to expires check, we should have on file, which can be touched.
	if this file is newer than expires time, do the "Last Modified" on remote pages
	(and later db entries), even if expires time is not over. (this would for example
	allow to touch this file, when you update your db and want immediate update without
	waiting until the cache expires)
	
2003-02-21 15:33  chregu

	* components/transformers/xslt.php:

	getting rid of sablotron part V
	- the xslt transformer now takes an option mode attribute, if set to
	mode="auto" it tries to figure out, which xslt processor is available,
	if libxslt is present, it takes that, otherwise it takes sabltron
	
	mode="libxslt" is also possible to force to use libxslt , even if it's not there (very useful...)
	
