2003-02-13 19:17  chregu

	* components/serializers/html.php:

	allow mode="dom" as attribute
	this will change the input to a domdocument, even if it's a string.
	Without it, strange things happen with libxslt compocachign
	(theoretically we could save the state, when the xml was saved and restore that back
	on cache loading, this would be the more elegant solution.. i'll make a bug)
	
2003-02-13 17:02  chregu

	* components/cache.php, sitemap/sitemap2php.xsl:

	- do not serialize $this->xml but do it in store() internally, otherwise we loose information
	and do unnecessary stuff during cache generation.
	- only load from cache, if $this->xml is not filled with some values before. from code-comment:
	
		load it
	           but just, if target is_null, if it's not null, we already have something in
	           $this->xml. This is mostly set, when a component before also had to regenerate
	           its data and can be mostly seen when we create a whole pipeline (eg. the generator
	            loads xml-data, then passes that to a transformer. There is no need to read the
	            content from the cache, if something like that happens. Moreover it leads to
	            problems with libxslt2/libxml internal handling, as it looses some info when
	            we serialize and deserialize xml-data (this has to be tested more thoroughly)
	
2003-02-13 16:58  chregu

	* sitemap/sitemap.php:

	register $this->xml
	
