2003-02-12 13:26  chregu

	* components/generators/structure2xml.php:

	caching of sql queries...
	- just add st2xmlCaching="true" as attribtue to <map:generate type="bitflux">
	and all you're sql queries are cached. This means, if the database didn't change, it gets
	the generated XML from the filesystem and does not generate it again..
	- Furthermore the sql-statements out of the structure are also cached. always. and only
	generated if your structure.xml does change.
	- Caching of aggregate queries is missing right now, will come later.
	
2003-02-12 13:15  chregu

	* components/transformers/mixedcontent.php:

	don't check for all entities, just for the obvious ones
	(has to be tested with our projects...)
	
2003-02-12 12:49  chregu

	* components/transformers/: phpprocessor.php, phpprocessorsax.php:

	- getting rid of sax stuff in phprocessor. it was far too slow. XPath
	approach is much faster.
	- If you want to use sax approache use phprocessorsax as transformer
	
